description._content: Yard no. 867. Outside of port wall showing landing stage, platform and ladders Date: 1910-1912 Taken from the Swan Hunter and Wigham Richardson Ltd. Shipbuilders Collection Reference no. DS.SWH/4/PH/7/9 (pg 15) This photograph was selected by Thomas Whittle as part of the 'Uncovering Archives Photography' Workshop held at Tyne and Wear Museums and Archives in November 2012.
